&lt;h1 id="the-equity-equation"&gt;The Equity Equation&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;July 2007&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An investor wants to give you money for a certain percentage of your startup. Should you take it? You&amp;rsquo;re about to hire your first employee. How much stock should you give him?&lt;/p&gt;
